<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a90e2, #d9534f);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .message {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .message h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }
        .course-info {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            color: #333;
        }
        .course-info h4 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 26px;
            margin: 0 0 15px;
        }
        .first-td, .second-td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .first-td {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #d9534f;
        }
        .second-td {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #333;
        }
        .total {
            font-size: 20px;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #d9534f;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #d9534f;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        td {
            padding: 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }
        .table-row {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .table-row td {
            border: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="message">
            <h1>Your Order is Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>Thank you for choosing EduMatrixAI!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="course-info">
            <h4>Here's What You Ordered:</h4>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>Order #: <%= order._id %></td>
                    <td>Order Date: <%= order.date %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td class="first-td">Item</td>
                    <td class="first-td">Qty</td>
                    <td class="first-td">Cost</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="second-td"><%= order.name %></td>
                    <td class="second-td">1</td>
                    <td class="second-td">$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <div class="table-row">
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Subtotal:</td>
                        <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Total:</td>
                        <td class="total">$<%= order.price %></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:edumatrixai@gmail.com">edumatrixai@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 EduMatrixAI. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
